verbs.description: [V: astros] roberto osuna pleased relieved by withdrawal of domestic assault charge the domestic assault charge against astros reliever roberto osuna was withdrawn in canadian court on tuesday after a crown prosecutor said available evidence yielded no reasonable prospect of conviction osuna entered into a one - year peace bond akin to a restraining order in the united states the peace bond prohibits osuna from contacting his alleged victim without her written consent for one year and mandates he continue counselling five hours before his team faced the blue jays and for the first time since the charge was levied osuna attended a hearing at old city hall in downtown toronto houston astros astros osuna assault roberto osuna
